This profile builds on CARINBBExplanationOfBenefit

Summary

Mandatory: 4 elements (7 nested mandatory elements)
Fixed Value: 10 elements
Prohibited: 25 elements

Slices

This structure defines the following Slices:

  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.supportingInfo is sliced based on the value of value:category (Closed)
  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.insurance is sliced based on the value of value:focal (Closed)
  • The element ExplanationOfBenefit.item.adjudication is sliced based on the value of value:category (Closed)
